OL,3,CGovernment to unveil cuts to benefits
OL,4,Camid backbench discontent
OL,6,FDowning Street has said there is a
OL,7,F"moral and an economic case" for an
OL,8,Foverhaul and that the changes would
OL,9,Fput the welfare system "back on a more
OL,10,Fsustainable path".
OL,12,FThere have been reports that the
OL,13,Fchanges could slash some #5 billion of
OL,14,Fwelfare payments.
OL,16,FBut there has been mounting unease on
OL,17,Fthe Labour Party's backbenches ahead
OL,18,Fof the anticipated changes, including
OL,19,Fover potential changes to the personal
OL,20,Findependence payment (PIP), the main
OL,21,Fdisability benefit.
