OL,3,CGovernment to unveil cuts to benefits
OL,4,Camid backbench discontent
OL,6,FYork Central MP Rachael Maskell has
OL,7,Fsaid she would be concerned if the
OL,8,FGovernment changed the eligibility
OL,9,Fcriteria to claim PIP.
OL,11,FLabour Greater Manchester mayor Andy
OL,12,FBurnham warned that changes to
OL,13,Feligibility and support while leaving
OL,14,Fthe system as it is would "trap too
OL,15,Fmany people in poverty".
