OL,3,CGovernment to unveil cuts to benefits
OL,4,Camid backbench discontent
OL,6,FReports suggest the scale of the
OL,7,Fbacklash has prompted a rethink of
OL,8,Frumoured plans to freeze the level of
OL,9,FPIP rather than increase it in line
OL,10,Fwith inflation, delivering a real-
OL,11,Fterms cut to 3.6 million claimants.
OL,13,FMs Kendall sought to reassure MPs on
OL,14,FMonday that the reforms would ensure
OL,15,F"trust and fairness" in the social
OL,16,Fsecurity system and make sure benefits
OL,17,Fare available "for people who need it
OL,18,Fnow, and for years to come".
