OL,3,CGovernment to unveil cuts to benefits
OL,4,Camid backbench discontent
OL,6,FMinisters insist that reform is
OL,7,Fnecessary, given the number of people
OL,8,Fin England and Wales claiming either
OL,9,Fsickness or disability benefit has
OL,10,Fsoared from 2.8 million to about 4.0
OL,11,Fmillion since 2019.
OL,13,FThe benefits bill has risen with this
OL,14,Fincrease, reaching #48 billion in 2023-
OL,15,F24, and is forecast to continue rising
OL,16,Fto #67 billion in 2029-30.
OL,18,FThat would exceed the current schools
OL,19,Fbudget.
