OL,3,CGovernment to unveil cuts to benefits
OL,4,Camid backbench discontent
OL,6,F"I think the Prime Minister has been
OL,7,Fclear there is both a moral and an
OL,8,Feconomic case for fixing our broken
OL,9,Fsocial security system that's holding
OL,10,Four people back, and our country
OL,11,Fback," the Prime Minister's official
OL,12,Fspokesman told reporters.
OL,14,F"That is why tomorrow the Government
OL,15,Fwill set out plans to overhaul the
OL,16,Fhealth and disability benefits system
OL,17,Fso it supports those who can work to
OL,18,Fdo so, while protecting those who are
OL,19,Fmost in need, and put the welfare
OL,20,Fsystem back on a more sustainable
OL,21,Fpath."
